00:37:16,460 --> 00:37:19,570
我去哪都行
I can go anywhere I want!

754
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,760
别
Don't do it!

755
00:37:31,780 --> 00:37:34,320
看来好东西也会嫌多
You really can have too much of a good thing.

756
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:14,930
空的
Nothing.

757
00:38:16,940 --> 00:38:18,350
你以为呢
What'd you expect?

758
00:38:18,680 --> 00:38:19,880
这儿可是哥谭
It's Gotham.

759
00:38:30,180 --> 00:38:31,420
我是玛希斯
It's Mathis.

760
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:33,600
我在大楼外  他们来了
I'm outside the site. They're here.

761
00:38:34,670 --> 00:38:37,160
不  还是别动他们
No. I think we should leave them be.

762
00:38:37,190 --> 00:38:38,760
他们在这儿什么都找不到
There's nothing here for them.

