Perhaps I am a bit jittery, sir.

774
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:51,210
很好
Good.

775
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:52,940
你该紧张
You should be.

776
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:57,360
如果我的手下出不来  你也别想活
'Cause if my boys don't make it, neither do you.

777
00:40:08,900 --> 00:40:11,770
吃瘪吧  法尔科内  你个孙子
Take that, Falcone, you son of a bitch!

778
00:40:11,770 --> 00:40:13,560
我说了  弗兰基
Huh? I told you, Frankie,

779
00:40:13,560 --> 00:40:14,710
这小子有两下
the kid's a player.

780
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:16,120
他有前途
He's got a future.

781
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:20,020
你像个老太太似的磨蹭什么呢  走啊
What are you waiting here like an old lady? Go!

782
00:40:28,790 --> 00:40:30,080
给我解开
Untie me.

783
00:40:32,910 --> 00:40:35,050
说"求你"
Say "pretty please."

784
00:40:36,950 --> 00:40:38,070
求你
Please.

785
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:49,210
有时候我觉得你不喜欢我
Sometimes I think you really don't like me.

786
00:40:49,950 --> 00:40:53,950
如果我不喜欢你  怎么会支持你接手
Now, would I be backing your takeover if I didn't like you?

787
00:40:54,750 --> 00:40:55,970
在法尔科内面前嘛
And that stuff with Falcone--

788
00:40:55,970 --> 00:40:57,870
总得装装样子给那老头看
well, we have to look good for the old man.

789
00:40:57,870 --> 00:41:00,450
如果他发现我们在合作
If he figures we're working together,

790
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,690
