we'd be cooked.

791
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,460
耐心点
Patience.

792
00:41:05,460 --> 00:41:07,580
我耐心快没了
I have no more patience.

793
00:41:07,860 --> 00:41:09,540
那老头必须死
The old man has to go.

794
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,380
我们得尽快出手
We must strike soon.

795
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,220
是啊
Yes. Mm.

796
00:41:15,480 --> 00:41:18,220
但要温柔一击
But softly.

797
00:42:04,070 --> 00:42:05,060
打扰
Excuse me.

798
00:42:06,580 --> 00:42:09,680
我听到了你哼的那首咏叹调
I couldn't help but overhear that aria you were humming.

799
00:42:09,770 --> 00:42:11,500
是啊  我最喜欢那首了
Oh, yes. It's my favorite.

800
00:42:11,510 --> 00:42:12,540
我也是
Mine, too.

801
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:16,240
那好啊
Ah, well, there you go.

802
00:42:16,950 --> 00:42:19,110
抱歉
I'm sorry, I-I just...

803
00:42:19,110 --> 00:42:21,180
我没想打扰你的
I-I didn't mean to bother you.

804
00:42:22,150 --> 00:42:24,540
我年轻时  我妈妈总给我唱这首曲子
My mother sang that to me when I was young.

805
00:42:24,810 --> 00:42:27,210
她这辈子  一直给我唱这首歌
Her whole life, she sang that to me.

806
00:42:27,780 --> 00:42:29,520
我好久没听过了
I hadn't heard it in a while, and I...

807
00:42:30,110 --> 00:42:32,160
都忍不住笑出来  你看上去...
I had to smile because you look...

808
00:42:34,700 --> 00:42:37,840
抱歉  我在瞎唠叨呢
Anyhow, sorry, I'm rambling on.

809
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:39,790
没事的
No, that's okay.

810
00:42:40,650 --> 00:42:41,850
你想听听吗
Do you want to listen?

811
00:42:43,500 --> 00:42:46,310
